text: Baygildy () is a rural locality (a selo) in Staroyantuzovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 378 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Baygildy
